  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beastie Land is a high-speed 2D platformer inspired by 90’s classics. Master precision platforming and explore vibrant levels to discover hidden treasures with your unique beast characters!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About Beastie Land</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Beastie Land, you’ll experience fast-paced, precision platforming action as you navigate through intricately designed levels brimming with hidden treasures and challenging obstacles. Choose from a variety of unique beast characters, each with their own special abilities, to help you conquer the game's dynamic environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy gameplay reminiscent of the golden age of platformers, but with a modern twist. Perfect your timing and reflexes to overcome tricky jumps and hazards while exploring expansive levels that hide secrets and valuable collectibles. Choose from a diverse roster of beast characters, each with unique skills to aid you on your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to jump, dash, and discover in Beastie Land—where every level is a new adventure!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beastie Land is a high-speed 2D platformer inspired by 90’s classics. Master precision platforming and explore vibrant levels to discover hidden treasures with your unique beast characters!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/154195b61af556e560b60924733d0375.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About Beastie Land</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Beastie Land, you’ll experience fast-paced, precision platforming action as you navigate through intricately designed levels brimming with hidden treasures and challenging obstacles. Choose from a variety of unique beast characters, each with their own special abilities, to help you conquer the game's dynamic environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/7973c9af897b5ac556347ed4eb914fe4.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy gameplay reminiscent of the golden age of platformers, but with a modern twist. Perfect your timing and reflexes to overcome tricky jumps and hazards while exploring expansive levels that hide secrets and valuable collectibles. Choose from a diverse roster of beast characters, each with unique skills to aid you on your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.poster.avif?t=1756486253\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.webm?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487900/extras/712ed531c70e3b32832211ea212c775d.mp4?t=1756486253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to jump, dash, and discover in Beastie Land—where every level is a new adventure!</p>",
